title: Dark Star Jarvan voicecover bug
body: i just got the new skin and its fantasitc but when i used it in one game i notice that the voicecover didnt change it stayed the same unlike the preview in youtube where is voice is more intimidating and more sinister please help...

replies.body: Hiya! Super sorry about this, Dark Star J4 is absolutely supposed to have VO processing. Everything will be hooked up and ready to roll in 8.6.
